(480, 1, '2016-09-17 14:47:45', '2016-09-17 14:47:45', 'If you wish to stay ahead of the curve, then you got to incorporate the best SEO strategies to improve your Google ranking.\r\n\r\nSo here here are some important SEO strategies that would help you beat the crowd on the road to success!\r\n\r\n<em><strong>1. Social Media:</strong></em>\r\nMarketers these days, use social media such as Facebook, Twitter and Linked In to support and boost their SEO. Thus, with the help of valuable social content you can optimize your page for maximum visibility and improve your ranking.\r\n\r\n<em><strong>2.Back-links:</strong></em>\r\nGenerating back-links can be used as a powerful tool to beat the competition. You can do this by writing for large publications, conducting industry interviews and hiring a public relations company to help you with the same.\r\n\r\n<strong><em>3.Mobile Friendly:</em></strong>\r\nHaving a mobile version of your website is a necessity in a world where the smart phones rule! Google, now ranks those websites much higher than the rest which apply SEO for their apps .\r\n\r\n<strong><em>4.Security:</em></strong>\r\nNow, make your websites secure by moving these to HTTPS, where “S” stands for security. Incorporating this feature would give you an edge over your competitors for sure.\r\n\r\n<strong><em>5.Adding markup:</em></strong>\r\nA type of markup known as “schema.org” helps Google know about your website details like company logo, type of company, location, reviews, etc. Including such a markup in the code of your website will pave way for a better ranking.\r\n\r\n<strong><em>6.Voice search:</em></strong>\r\nPeople nowadays, prefer the voice search function as they find it more convenient to use. Therefore, you need to make sure that your content can be searched easily through the voice search function. Remember to use those keywords that are more likely to be spoken.\r\n\r\nNow, climb up the ladder of success with these SEO strategies!\r\n\r\n<strong> </strong>', 'WHAT ARE THE EEFECTIVE SEO STRATEGIES IN 2016?', '', 'publish', 'open', 'open', '', 'what-are-the-eefective-seo-strategies-in-2016', '', '', '2016-09-20 05:45:55', '2016-09-20 05:45:55', '', 0, 'http://livedemos.wpengine.com/iodtheme/?p=480', 0, 'post', '', 0),
(481, 1, '2016-09-13 14:57:18', '2016-09-13 14:57:18', '<p style="text-align: justify;">This is perhaps one of the toughest decisions that one has to make. The website forms the online face of your company so it has to be the best and at the same time better than the rest too.</p>\r\n<p style="text-align: justify;">Some vital points that you shouldn’t miss out on!</p>\r\n<p style="text-align: justify;"><em><strong>1. Clarity of Goals:</strong></em></p>\r\n<p style="text-align: justify;">Having a clarity of the Goals, Aims and the Objectives of the organization helps you choose the web development company that best serves your needs.</p>\r\n<p style="text-align: justify;"><em><strong>2.Quality of the Web Design:</strong></em></p>\r\n<p style="text-align: justify;">Quality should always be a priority while choosing a web development company. Always go for the one that provides you with an amazing and impressive web design. The quality of the website design should be such that makes a memorable impression and gives you an edge over the competitors.</p>\r\n<p style="text-align: justify;"><em><strong>3.Cost Effectiveness:</strong></em></p>\r\n<p style="text-align: justify;">Cost effectiveness adds more to your efficiency. You should be aware of how much you are capable of spending. So, plan your budget accordingly and make a choice.</p>\r\n<p style="text-align: justify;"><em><strong>4.User Interface and Clientele:</strong></em></p>\r\n<p style="text-align: justify;">A good user interface helps you increase your customer base. So, it definitely forms an important part of the website. Therefore, you must ask the company to provide you with the user interface of those websites that have been created for other clients. Also, cross check the references of the existing clientele and see what the references say about the company.</p>\r\n<p style="text-align: justify;"><em><strong>5.Measuring the success rate:</strong></em></p>\r\n<p style="text-align: justify;">The method that the company uses to measure results also plays a vital role in the selection process. Make sure that there is a proper use of the analytic tools.</p>\r\n<p style="text-align: justify;">Never let these facts slip off your mind and have the best web development company by your side!</p>', 'WHAT ARE THE BASIC THINGS TO REMEMBER WHILE CHOOSING A WEB DEVELOPMENT COMPANY?', '', 'publish', 'open', 'open', '', 'what-are-the-basic-things-to-remember-while-choosing-a-web-development-company', '', '', '2016-09-13 15:54:01', '2016-09-13 15:54:01', '', 0, 'http://livedemos.wpengine.com/iodtheme/?p=481', 0, 'post', '', 0),
