(726, 1, '2016-08-17 18:05:40', '2016-08-17 18:05:40', '[vc_row][vc_column][vc_empty_space height="30px"][tt_iod_title_shortcode title="Our services" title_size="24" title_color="#0a0a0a"][vc_empty_space height="25px"][/vc_column][/vc_row][vc_row][vc_column offset="vc_col-lg-4 vc_col-md-4 vc_col-xs-12"][tt_iod_icon_box_shortcode insert_graphic="icon" icon_fontawesome="fa fa-code" alignment="center" show_link="yes" add_title="Web Development" add_text="Give you business a face with a website. We provide high end web development services in PHP, WordPress, .Net, X-Cart, Magento, and Shopify. Our team of expert developers will carefully analyze your need to give you best options to choose from. We have more than 10 years of experience with Web Development and we have delivered more than 1000 websites so far.\r\n\r\nBest thing about our development team is that we are aware of Search Engine Optimization and we always put only Search Engine Friendly elements in website. This ensures easy crawling and indexing of website. To know more about our expertise contact us." add_image="486" add_btn_1="Contact Us" add_btn_link_1="/contact/" title="Web DEVELOPMENT"]Custom Web Development services to meet your need at reasonable cost.[/tt_iod_icon_box_shortcode][tt_iod_icon_box_shortcode insert_graphic="icon" icon_fontawesome="fa fa-mobile" alignment="center" show_link="yes" add_title="Mobile Application Development" add_text="We provide custom Mobile Application Development services to shape your concept into reality. We have over 6 years of experience with mobile application development for IOS and Android devices. So far we have built more than 200 applications for IOS and Android devices.\r\n\r\nThe best thing about our company is that we work very closely with our customers to ensure that the flow and design of the application is as per customer''s need. To know more about our services contact us." add_image="486" add_btn_1="Contact Us" add_btn_link_1="/contact/" title="Mobile Application Development"]Custom Mobile Application Development to shape your concept into reality.[/tt_iod_icon_box_shortcode][/vc_column][vc_column offset="vc_col-lg-4 vc_col-md-4 vc_col-xs-12"][tt_iod_icon_box_shortcode insert_graphic="icon" icon_fontawesome="fa fa-html5" alignment="center" show_link="yes" add_title="Web Designing" add_text="Amicron Soft Solutions has been working with businesses and organizations for more than 10 years to create professional websites at competitive prices. We are passionate about designing websites and we work very closely with you to ensure your website reflects your business in a unique and professional way.\r\n\r\nWe are very confident in our skills and that is why we offer infinite revisions of design. Our motive is to provide 100% satisfaction to our customers. To know more about our services contact us." add_image="486" add_btn_1="Contact Us" add_btn_link_1="/contact/" title="Web Designing"]Responsive web designing services to portrait your business efficiently.[/tt_iod_icon_box_shortcode][tt_iod_icon_box_shortcode insert_graphic="icon" icon_fontawesome="fa fa-weixin" alignment="center" show_link="yes" add_title="Online Reputation Management" add_text="Are you facing some negative results popping up in top search results of Google and other search engines while you search for your business? It''s very frustrating to deal with such negative results and it is even harmful for our business. We can do nothing except looking at our website''s traffic/conversions going down. Is this true? Not anymore because this is something we can help you with.\r\n\r\nWe have more than 8 years of experience with managing online reputation for our customer''s businesses. We know what is takes to bring negative results down and to bring some positive news about our business. Contact us to know more about how we do it. " add_image="486" add_btn_1="Contact Us" add_btn_link_1="/contact/" title="Online Reputation Management"]Online Reputation Manage