c_col-md-6 vc_col-xs-12"][tt_iod_icon_box_shortcode insert_graphic="icon" icon_fontawesome="fa fa-rocket" size="sm" title_tag="h5" title="OUR MISSION"]Our mission is to enhance the business of our customers with creative Design, Development and marketing within reasonable cost. We are very friendly in our dealings to the customers and it helps us retain existing clients and expand customer circle.[/tt_iod_icon_box_shortcode][vc_empty_space height="15px"][/vc_column_inner][/vc_row_inner][/vc_column][/vc_row][vc_row full_width="stretch_row" css=".vc_custom_1459244281542{background-color: #f7f7f7 !important;}"][vc_column][tt_iod_title_shortcode alignment="text-left" title="COMPANY HISTORY"][vc_empty_space height="60px"][tt_iod_history_shortcode tabs="%5B%7B%22year%22%3A%221907%22%7D%2C%7B%22year%22%3A%221914%22%7D%2C%7B%22year%22%3A%221917%22%7D%2C%7B%22year%22%3A%221948%22%7D%2C%7B%22year%22%3A%221956%22%7D%2C%7B%22year%22%3A%221968%22%7D%2C%7B%22year%22%3A%221971%22%7D%5D"][tt_iod_history_item_shortcode]\r\n<h6><img class="alignleft wp-image-740 size-medium" src="http://www.amicronsoftsolutions.com/wp-content/uploads/2016/03/Shilong-172-1-300x169.jpg" width="300" height="169" /></h6>\r\n<h6>August 11, 1987</h6>\r\n<h5 class="title">DeepaK Tyagi is Born</h5>\r\nDeepak Tyagi born on 11 August, 1987 in Agra, Uttar Pradesh (India). He was very ambitious since childhood and keen to learn new things.[/tt_iod_history_item_shortcode][tt_iod_history_item_shortcode]\r\n<h6><img class="alignleft wp-image-192 size-full" src="http://livedemos.wpengine.com/iodtheme/wp-content/uploads/sites/5/2016/03/time-line-img.jpg" alt="time-line-img" width="401" height="226" /> July 21, 2009</h6>\r\n<h5 class="title">Deepak completed his Bachelor''s</h5>\r\nOn July 21, 2009 Deepak completed his Bachelor''s in Computer Applications from Institute of Basic Science (Agra). His name was in top 3 students of his institute.[/tt_iod_history_item_shortcode][tt_iod_history_item_shortcode]\r\n<h6><img class="alignleft wp-image-192 size-full" src="http://livedemos.wpengine.com/iodtheme/wp-content/uploads/sites/5/2016/03/time-line-img.jpg" alt="time-line-img" width="401" height="226" />August 10, 2009</h6>\r\n<h5 class="title">Deepak joined Sebiz Infotech as Marketing Trainee</h5>\r\nOn August 10, 2009 Deepak joined Sebiz Infotech (Mohali) as Internet Marketing trainee. He was about to start his journey with Online Marketing and his first day of training was also his birthday. He was very excited about his training.[/tt_iod_history_item_shortcode][tt_iod_history_item_shortcode]\r\n<h6><img class="alignleft wp-image-192 size-full" src="http://livedemos.wpengine.com/iodtheme/wp-content/uploads/sites/5/2016/03/time-line-img.jpg" alt="time-line-img" width="401" height="226" />February 21, 2010</h6>\r\n<h5 class="title">Deepak has been appointed as Internet Marketing Expert</h5>\r\nOn February 21, 2010 Deepak had been appointed as Internet Marketing Expert at Sebiz Infotech (Mohali). He completed his 6 months of training in marketing and had been placed successfully in the same company. He was the topper of his batch. He joined Product Marketing Team of Sebiz.[/tt_iod_history_item_shortcode][tt_iod_history_item_shortcode]\r\n<h6><img class="alignleft wp-image-192 size-full" src="http://livedemos.wpengine.com/iodtheme/wp-content/uploads/sites/5/2016/03/time-line-img.jpg" alt="time-line-img" width="401" height="226" />November 21, 2011</h6>\r\n<h5 class="title">Deepak joined Cogniter Technologies</h5>\r\nOn November 21, 2011 Deepak switched his job and had been appointed as Team Leader - Online Marketing with Cogniter Technologies (Chandigarh). He was managing a team of Internet Marketing Experts at Cogniter and he had started taking care of client interactions.[/tt_iod_history_item_shortcode][tt_iod_history_item_shortcode]\r\n<h6><img class="alignleft wp-image-192 size-full" src="http://livedemos.wpengine.com/iodtheme/wp-content/uploads/sites/5/2016/03/time-line-img.jpg" alt="time-line-img" width="401" height="226" /> June 14, 2012</h6>\r\n<h5 class="title">Deepak joined Netsmartz Infotech</h5>\r\nOn June 14, 2o12 Deepak joined Netsmartz Infotech as Project Lead in Online Marketing. He was handing 2 most important in house project of his company with the help of a team.[/tt_iod_history_item_shortcode][tt_iod_history_item_shortcode]\r\n<h6><img class="alignleft wp-image-192 size-full" src="http://livedemos.wpengine.com/iodtheme/wp-content/uploads/sites/5/2016/03/time-line-img.jpg" alt="time-line-img" width="401" height="226" /> February 9, 2015</h6>\r\n<h5 class="title">Deepak joined InfraWebSoft Technologies</h5>\r\nOn February 9, 2015 Deepak joined InfraWebSoft Technologies as Manager - Online Marketing. Within a month he was promoted as Head - Project Delivery. He was managing Online Marketing and Business Development department at InfraWebSoft Technologies.[/tt_iod_history_item_shortcode][tt_iod_history_item_shortcode]\r\n<h6><img class="alignleft wp-image-192 size-full" src="http://livedemos.wpengine.com/iodtheme/wp-content/uploads/sites/5/2016/03/time-line-img.jpg" alt="time-line-img" width="401" height="226" /> July 11, 2015</h6>\r\n<h5 class="title">Deepak joined Amicron Soft Solutions as CEO</h5>\r\nOn July 11, 2015 Deepak joined Amicron Soft Solutions as CEO. Finally he had got into where he was meant to. This is how we wanted to see him and we are pleased he is finally here to lead our organization to success.[/tt_iod_history_item_shortcode][/tt_iod_history_shortcode][vc_empty_space height="40px"][/vc_column][/vc_row][vc_row full_width="stretch_row" css=".vc_custom_1459244933785{background-image: url(http://livedemos.wpengine.com/iodtheme/wp-content/uploads/sites/5/2016/03/client-bg.jpg?id=40) !important;}"][vc_column][tt_iod_title_shortcode title="OUR AMAZING CLIENTS" show_sb="yes" sbtitle="WE TRUST IN LONGLASTING PARTNERSHIPS WITH THE MOST IMPORTANT BRANDS ON THE MARKET"][vc_empty_space height="30px"][tt_iod_brands_shortcode][tt_iod_brands_item_shortcode image_1="664" link_1="http://www.vitasciences.com" image_2="652" link_2="http://www.plumdragonherbs.com" image_3="653" link_3="http://www.nusportswear.com" image_4="654" link_4="http://www.mytat.com" image_5="655" link_5="http://www.morraudio.com"][tt_iod_brands_item_shortcode image_1="656" link_1="http://www.maximumk9service.com" image_2="657" link_2="http://www.inhairit.com" image_3="676" link_3="http://www.hopewindhealth.com/" image_4="665" link_4="http://www.dylninspired.com" image_5="659" link_5="http://www.apachepowerboats.com"][tt_iod_brands_item_shortcode image_1="667" link_1="http://www.aignerart.com/" image_2="668" link_2="http://www.bizfind.us" image_3="670" link_3="http://www.casinonetworkinc.com" image_4="671" link_4="http://www.duxsports.com/" image_5="674" link_5="http://www.greengurunutrition.com/"][tt_iod_brands_item_shortcode image_1="678" link_1="http://www.mastagriculture.com/" image_2="679" link_2="http://www.medusasmakeup.com/" image_3="680" link_3="http://www.methodfitness.com/" image_4="681" link_4="http://www.presidential-training.com/" image_5="682" link_5="http://www.privilegeclothing.com/"][tt_iod_brands_item_shortcode image_1="684" link_1="http://www.remi-d.com/" image_2="685" link_2="http://www.rootsbid.com/" image_3="689" link_3="http://www.sonarajewelry.com/" image_4="690" link_4="http://www.parklanes.net/" image_5="691" link_5="http://www.pricebeat.ca"][/tt_iod_brands_shortcode][vc_empty_space height="30px"][/vc_column][/vc_row]', 'About', '', 'inherit', 'closed', 'closed', '', '189-revision-v1', '', '', '2016-09-07 06:14:49', '2016-09-07 06:14:49', '', 189, 'http://www.amicronsoftsolutions.com/189-revision-v1/', 0, 'revision', '', 0),
