(758, 1, '2016-09-13 05:21:50', '2016-09-13 05:21:50', 'This is perhaps one of the toughest decisions that one has to make. The website forms the online face of your company so it has to be the best and at the same time better than the rest too.\r\n\r\nSome vital points that you shouldn’t miss out on!\r\n<ul>\r\n 	<li><strong>Clarity of Goals:</strong></li>\r\n</ul>\r\nHaving a clarity of the Goals, Aims and the Objectives of the organization helps you choose the web development company that best serves your needs.\r\n<ul>\r\n 	<li><strong>Quality of the Web Design:</strong></li>\r\n</ul>\r\nQuality should always be a priority while choosing a web development company. Always go for the one that provides you with an amazing and impressive web design. The quality of the website design should be such that makes a memorable impression and gives you an edge over the competitors.\r\n<ul>\r\n 	<li><strong>Cost Effectiveness:</strong></li>\r\n</ul>\r\nCost effectiveness adds more to your efficiency. You should be aware of how much you are capable of spending. So, plan your budget accordingly and make a choice.\r\n<ul>\r\n 	<li><strong>User Interface and Clientele:</strong></li>\r\n</ul>\r\nA good user interface helps you increase your customer base. So, it definitely forms an important part of the website. Therefore, you must ask the company to provide you with the user interface of those websites that have been created for other clients. Also, cross check the references of the existing clientele and see what the references say about the company.\r\n<ul>\r\n 	<li><strong>Measuring the success rate:</strong></li>\r\n</ul>\r\nThe method that the company uses to measure results also plays a vital role in the selection process. Make sure that there is a proper use of the analytic tools.\r\n\r\nNever let these facts slip off your mind and have the best web development company by your side!', 'WHAT ARE THE BASIC THINGS TO REMEMBER WHILE CHOOSING A WEB DEVELOPMENT COMPANY?', '', 'inherit', 'closed', 'closed', '', '481-revision-v1', '', '', '2016-09-13 05:21:50', '2016-09-13 05:21:50', '', 481, 'http://www.amicronsoftsolutions.com/481-revision-v1/', 0, 'revision', '', 0),
(759, 1, '2016-09-13 05:38:05', '2016-09-13 05:38:05', '<p style="text-align: justify;">This is perhaps one of the toughest decisions that one has to make. The website forms the online face of your company so it has to be the best and at the same time better than the rest too.</p>\r\n<p style="text-align: justify;">Some vital points that you shouldn’t miss out on!</p>\r\n\r\n<ul style="text-align: justify;">\r\n 	<li><strong>Clarity of Goals:</strong></li>\r\n</ul>\r\n<p style="text-align: justify;">Having a clarity of the Goals, Aims and the Objectives of the organization helps you choose the web development company that best serves your needs.</p>\r\n\r\n<ul style="text-align: justify;">\r\n 	<li><strong>Quality of the Web Design:</strong></li>\r\n</ul>\r\n<p style="text-align: justify;">Quality should always be a priority while choosing a web development company. Always go for the one that provides you with an amazing and impressive web design. The quality of the website design should be such that makes a memorable impression and gives you an edge over the competitors.</p>\r\n\r\n<ul style="text-align: justify;">\r\n 	<li><strong>Cost Effectiveness:</strong></li>\r\n</ul>\r\n<p style="text-align: justify;">Cost effectiveness adds more to your efficiency. You should be aware of how much you are capable of spending. So, plan your budget accordingly and make a choice.</p>\r\n\r\n<ul style="text-align: justify;">\r\n 	<li><strong>User Interface and Clientele:</strong></li>\r\n</ul>\r\n<p style="text-align: justify;">A good user interface helps you increase your customer base. So, it definitely forms an important part of the website. Therefore, you must ask the company to provide you with the user interface of those websites that have been created for other clients. Also, cross check the references of the existing clientele and see what the references say about the company.</p>\r\n\r\n<ul style="text-align: justify;">\r\n 	<li><strong>Measuring the success rate:</stro