(762, 1, '2016-09-20 05:27:27', '2016-09-20 05:27:27', '&nbsp;\r\n\r\n<span style="color: #000000;">If you wish to stay ahead of the curve, then you got to incorporate the best SEO strategies to improve your Google ranking.</span>\r\n\r\n<span style="color: #000000;">So here here are some important SEO strategies that would help you beat the crowd on the road to success!</span>\r\n\r\n<em><strong>1. Social Media:</strong></em>\r\nMarketers these days, use social media such as Facebook, Twitter and Linked In to support and boost their SEO. Thus, with the help of valuable social content you can optimize your page for maximum visibility and improve your ranking.\r\n\r\n<em><strong>2.Back-links:</strong></em>\r\nGenerating back-links can be used as a powerful tool to beat the competition. You can do this by writing for large publications, conducting industry interviews and hiring a public relations company to help you with the same.\r\n\r\n<strong><em>3.Mobile Friendly:</em></strong>\r\nHaving a mobile version of your website is a necessity in a world where the smart phones rule! Google, now ranks those websites much higher than the rest which apply SEO for their apps .\r\n\r\n<strong><em>4.Security:</em></strong>\r\nNow, make your websites secure by moving these to HTTPS, where “S” stands for security. Incorporating this feature would give you an edge over your competitors for sure.\r\n\r\n<strong><em>5.Adding markup:</em></strong>\r\nA type of markup known as “schema.org” helps Google know about your website details like company logo, type of company, location, reviews, etc. Including such a markup in the code of your website will pave way for a better ranking.\r\n\r\n<strong><em>6.Voice search:</em></strong>\r\nPeople nowadays, prefer the voice search function as they find it more convenient to use. Therefore, you need to make sure that your content can be searched easily through the voice search function. Remember to use those keywords that are more likely to be spoken.\r\n\r\nNow, climb up the ladder of success with these SEO strategies!\r\n\r\n<strong> </strong>', 'WHAT ARE THE EEFECTIVE SEO STRATEGIES IN 2016?', '', 'inherit', 'closed', 'closed', '', '480-autosave-v1', '', '', '2016-09-20 05:27:27', '2016-09-20 05:27:27', '', 480, 'http://www.amicronsoftsolutions.com/480-autosave-v1/', 0, 'revision', '', 0),
