(772, 1, '2016-10-06 08:54:18', '2016-10-06 08:54:18', '<p style="text-align: justify;">Good reputation is something a company cannot do without. So, if you are about to hire an Online Reputation Management (ORM) firm that would help you reach the pinnacle of success, then don’t forget to follow these guidelines:</p>\r\n<p style="text-align: justify;"></p>\r\n<p style="text-align: justify;"><strong>1. Credibility of the Firm:</strong></p>\r\n<p style="text-align: justify;"><strong> </strong>The first and the foremost thing that needs to be checked is the credibility of the firm. So, make sure that you go through all the track records of the firm. These records would help you know how experienced the firm is in its field and also about the performance during the past years.</p>\r\n<p style="text-align: justify;"><strong>2. Types of Services offered:</strong></p>\r\n<p style="text-align: justify;"><strong> </strong>The next step is to inquire about the types of services offered. Most of the firms have a single plan for all. So, choosing such a firm would definitely be a bad decision. Instead, go for the one that meets all your requirements.</p>\r\n<p style="text-align: justify;"><strong>3. Cost:</strong></p>\r\n<p style="text-align: justify;">Cost is yet another important factor that needs to be taken into account. If the price quoted by the firm might upset your budget in the long run, then you should drop the idea right away.</p>\r\n<p style="text-align: justify;"><strong>4. Beware of False Promises:</strong></p>\r\n<p style="text-align: justify;"><strong> </strong>Some companies may come up with claims like “success guaranteed” in a short span of time. But, in reality these are nothing but false promises to lure the customers. So, beware of such firms!</p>\r\n<p style="text-align: justify;"><strong>5. A Big No to Black Hat SEO:</strong></p>\r\n<p style="text-align: justify;"><strong> </strong>Stay away from the firms that use aggressive SEO strategies. These do more harm than any good as they just aim at quick financial returns without even paying a heed to the SEO guidelines.</p>\r\n<p style="text-align: justify;">So, settle for nothing but the best as the reputation says it all!</p>', 'How To Choose The Right Online Reputation Management Firm?', '', 'publish', 'open', 'open', '', 'how-to-choose-the-right-online-reputation-management-firm', '', '', '2016-10-06 08:54:18', '2016-10-06 08:54:18', '', 0, 'http://www.amicronsoftsolutions.com/?p=772', 0, 'post', '', 0),
