(805, 1, '2016-11-29 09:44:24', '2016-11-29 09:44:24', '<p style="text-align: justify;">Mobile apps are the latest trend! From learning to making online payments, we depend heavily on these. This makes it necessary to come up with the mobile apps that are really user friendly.</p>\r\n<p style="text-align: justify;">Some important facts in this regard are:</p>\r\n<p style="text-align: justify;"><em><strong>1.Chalk out a Plan:</strong></em>\r\nA plan with a purpose is what you need. Clarity of ideas is always going to help you in the long run. Decide about the type of app you wish to create and the category to which your app belongs.</p>\r\n<p style="text-align: justify;"><em><strong>2.Be Unique:</strong></em>\r\nTo create a niche for yourself, you have to be unique in everything you do. So, welcome those ideas that make you better than the rest. A proper survey on the likes and preferences of the users would be of a great help.</p>\r\n<p style="text-align: justify;"><em><strong>3.Target group:</strong></em>\r\nThis is another important fact to be considered while creating an app. If the app is iPhone specific, then build the same for iTunes stores. But, if you wish to promote your business, then Google Play Store should be your choice.\r\nIf the app serves all the target groups, then it is advisable to go for one group first, analyze the performance and then move ahead.</p>\r\n<p style="text-align: justify;"><em><strong>4.Designing &amp; Coding:</strong></em>\r\nYou may use simple software and tools and also take the help of video lessons on the internet to design your app .\r\nIn case, you are not well versed with the coding skills, then ask the experts to help you out.</p>\r\n<p style="text-align: justify;"><em><strong>5.Feedback:</strong></em>\r\nFeedback is very important as it helps you to improve upon your skills constantly. So, develop small apps initially, take the user’s feedback seriously and work on fixing the bugs. The more satisfied your customers are, the more successful you will be.</p>\r\n<p style="text-align: justify;">So, get started on creating one of the top rated apps!</p>', 'HOW TO CREATE THE BEST MOBILE APP?', '', 'publish', 'open', 'open', '', 'how-to-create-the-best-mobile-app-2', '', '', '2016-11-29 09:44:24', '2016-11-29 09:44:24', '', 0, 'http://www.amicronsoftsolutions.com/?p=805', 0, 'post', '', 0),
